1
00:00:05,960 --> 00:00:08,667
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,667 --> 00:00:12,122
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,122 --> 00:00:18,315
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,315 --> 00:00:24,541
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,541 --> 00:00:31,062
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,062 --> 00:00:36,048
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,048 --> 00:00:43,348
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,348 --> 00:00:48,372
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,372 --> 00:00:49,885
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,885 --> 00:00:55,648
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,648 --> 00:01:02,148
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,148 --> 00:01:08,515
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,515 --> 00:01:11,824
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:11,824 --> 00:01:13,303
Gao Yang!

15
00:01:13,303 --> 00:01:15,466
Gao Yang, what are you doing?

16
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:19,366
Stop dilly-dallying! You're going to be late, Gao Yang!

17
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:25,624
Gao Yang, are you still in there?

18
00:01:25,624 --> 00:01:27,883
Don't try to jump out the window!

19
00:01:27,883 --> 00:01:30,043
There's a trash can down there!

20
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:33,503
It's useless even if you go to the train station! I have eyes everywhere!

21
00:01:33,503 --> 00:01:34,603
Gao Yang!

22
00:01:34,603 --> 00:01:36,395
Gao...

23
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:44,096
Hello, Xiaowen.

24
00:01:44,096 --> 00:01:46,604
Gao Bin. Hi, Mr. Gao.

25
00:01:46,604 --> 00:01:51,264
Gao Yang, you... What's this about?

26
00:01:51,264 --> 00:01:54,983
Mr. Gao, don't speak to me like that.

27
00:01:54,983 --> 00:01:57,523
I'm no longer the naughty Gao Yang from before.

28
00:01:57,523 --> 00:01:59,004
Then you are...

29
00:01:59,004 --> 00:02:01,124
A wise man.

30
00:02:01,124 --> 00:02:02,943
I had an epiphany.

31
00:02:02,943 --> 00:02:08,743
I can only rely on myself to go to Beijing.

32
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:16,624
Sure. That's big talk.

33
00:02:16,624 --> 00:02:19,003
I mean what I said this time.

34
00:02:19,003 --> 00:02:21,064
Great!

35
00:02:21,064 --> 00:02:23,423
Xiaowen, let's go.

36
00:02:23,423 --> 00:02:25,218
Let's go and strive for success.

37
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,123
Hurry up.

38
00:02:27,123 --> 00:02:29,404
Single-celled organism (simple-minded).

39
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,160
[Wisdom, Enthusiasm, and Diligence]

40
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:34,403
I have an announcement to make before class.

41
00:02:34,403 --> 00:02:37,603
There's a new transfer student in our class.

42
00:02:37,603 --> 00:02:39,403
He just came back from Beijing.

43
00:02:39,403 --> 00:02:42,904
He didn't do very well before. You should all know him very well.

44
00:02:42,904 --> 00:02:46,864
I hope everyone will give him a chance to get reacquainted.

45
00:02:46,864 --> 00:02:48,729
Come on in.

46
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,164
- Hello, Mr. Wu.
- Hello.

47
00:02:54,164 --> 00:02:55,523
Hello, Everyone.

48
00:02:55,523 --> 00:02:57,003
Say it under the podium.

49
00:02:57,003 --> 00:02:58,449
Okay.

50
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,333
Introduce yourself.

51
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,239
Hello, Fellow Classmates.

52
00:03:07,239 --> 00:03:08,563
My name is Gao Yang.

53
00:03:08,563 --> 00:03:12,763
From now on, I will officially be a part of this group.

54
00:03:12,763 --> 00:03:17,804
Together, we will prepare for the college entrance exam and embrace the future.

55
00:03:17,804 --> 00:03:19,816
I've finished talking.

56
00:03:19,816 --> 00:03:22,170
Look at their enthusiastic response.

57
00:03:22,170 --> 00:03:26,263
Gao Yang, if you can't go to Beijing, then you should just study in Tieyuan.

58
00:03:26,263 --> 00:03:29,743
No, Old Wu. Beijing is still my goal.

59
00:03:29,743 --> 00:03:34,084
Classmates, let's work hard together. Keep it up.

60
00:03:34,084 --> 00:03:35,763
Sure. It's quite aspiring and ambitious.

61
00:03:35,763 --> 00:03:39,504
The midterms are coming. It's a good chance to prove yourself.

62
00:03:39,504 --> 00:03:41,415
Okay.

63
00:03:41,415 --> 00:03:44,333
Go on, return to your seat. No one touched it.

64
00:03:44,333 --> 00:03:45,798
Okay.

65
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:48,563
Hello.

66
00:03:48,563 --> 00:03:51,324
What's wrong with Gao Yang?

67
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,044
He lost his mind.

68
00:03:53,044 --> 00:03:56,164
All right, open your books to Thunderstorm by Cao Yu. (a Chinese play about a family's downfall due to incest)

69
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,810
What's wrong? You're not happy that he's back?

70
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:01,820
My goodness.

71
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:04,860
One moment he's leaving, and then he's staying.

72
00:04:04,863 --> 00:04:06,538
I'm tired of it.

73
00:04:11,740 --> 00:04:14,623
Hello, Classmate. My name is Gao Yang.

74
00:04:14,623 --> 00:04:17,924
From now on, we'll be desk mates.

75
00:04:17,924 --> 00:04:20,224
Let's cultivate our friendship.

76
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:25,187
The teachers asked you to make up your homework.

77
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:45,373
I knew it.

78
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:49,744
Let's go get water.

79
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:02,484
Xiaowen. Xiaowen, since when was he like this?

80
00:05:02,484 --> 00:05:04,439
This morning.

81
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,664
It will pass soon.

82
00:05:06,664 --> 00:05:09,584
- What?
- Watch this.

83
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,534
Gao Yang, it's lunch time!

84
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:16,963
It's lunch time?

85
00:05:16,963 --> 00:05:19,028
We just finished the class.

86
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:22,523
Wait, why didn't you wake me up?

87
00:05:22,523 --> 00:05:24,544
Why should I wake you?

88
00:05:24,544 --> 00:05:28,083
You're my desk mate. You should urge me to study hard.

89
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:32,524
Why should I urge you to study?

90
00:05:32,524 --> 00:05:34,923
I would also urge you to study, too.

91
00:05:34,923 --> 00:05:37,684
Desk mates should help each other.

92
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,452
You're too apathetic.

93
00:05:40,452 --> 00:05:42,230
I don't need it.

94
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,084
Why are you being so pompous?

95
00:05:45,084 --> 00:05:47,363
Your grades are just mediocre.

96
00:05:47,363 --> 00:05:50,663
I saw your score from the last exam. It was just average.

97
00:05:50,663 --> 00:05:52,904
What are you so arrogant about?

98
00:05:52,904 --> 00:05:55,964
Everyone needs help sometimes.

99
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:25,548
I'll give you an eye-opener at noon.

100
00:06:25,548 --> 00:06:30,071
[Episode 10: Constantly Making Aspirations, But No Long-Term Aspirations]

101
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,924
Hurry, keep up.

102
00:06:32,924 --> 00:06:34,984
Mr. Gao, I can't run anymore.

103
00:06:34,984 --> 00:06:37,144
Exactly, Brother Bin. Let us do free activities.

104
00:06:37,144 --> 00:06:40,540
You wish! Your health is the most important thing, understand?

105
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,303
You'll know when you're in your 30s.

106
00:06:42,303 --> 00:06:44,884
Faster! Stick out your chest and chins up. Be more energetic!

107
00:06:44,884 --> 00:06:47,843
One, two, one. One, two, one.

108
00:06:47,843 --> 00:06:50,188
One, two...

109
00:06:50,188 --> 00:06:53,564
Dawei, what are you doing? Why aren't you in class?

110
00:06:58,780 --> 00:07:00,362
Dawei!

111
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:14,984
Let me tell you, Zhang Wuji, Linghu Chong, Naruto Uzumaki, Kurosaki Ichigo,

112
00:07:14,984 --> 00:07:17,723
which one of them didn't become the lead character because of a secret scripture?

113
00:07:17,723 --> 00:07:20,703
For someone as smart as me, why don't I have good grades?

114
00:07:20,703 --> 00:07:23,010
Because I don't have a secret scripture.

115
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:29,384
What do you want for lunch? I'll go get the food.

116
00:07:29,384 --> 00:07:31,483
Wait, how do you still have an appetite for food?

117
00:07:31,483 --> 00:07:33,864
We're not doing well in school.

118
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,498
No, don't touch it. This is a secret code.

119
00:07:38,498 --> 00:07:40,823
What secret code?

120
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,843
Did you bring the money?

121
00:07:46,843 --> 00:07:48,710
I want to see the goods.

122
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,400
How can I see it clearly if you flip through it so fast?

123
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:55,786
Hurry up. If you speak nonsense again, I'm not selling it.

124
00:07:55,786 --> 00:07:57,558
Here, here.

125
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:06,903
- Wait, give it to me.
- That's not enough money.

126
00:08:06,903 --> 00:08:10,284
What do you mean not enough? Just take it. I'm an old customer. Come on.

127
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,084
- I won't sell it if you don't have the money.
- Wait.

128
00:08:14,084 --> 00:08:17,504
Old Piao. Old Piao! Old Piao!

129
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:21,423
Enough with those heretical ideas.

130
00:08:21,423 --> 00:08:24,684
No, you don't understand. Xiaowen.

131
00:08:24,684 --> 00:08:27,763
Those are notes from Top Scorer Wu Zhixun!

132
00:08:27,763 --> 00:08:29,584
Who's Wu Zhixun?

133
00:08:29,584 --> 00:08:33,068
He went to Beijing University. Beijing University! Beijing University, do you understand?

134
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,084
There's really such a person?

135
00:08:35,084 --> 00:08:37,429
You can ask around if you don't believe me.

136
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:44,104
Xiaowen, lend me some money. I almost have enough.

137
00:08:44,104 --> 00:08:47,363
If you want to buy study materials, go ask Mr. Gao for it.

138
00:08:47,363 --> 00:08:50,463
No, why should I ask him? I said I can do it by myself.

139
00:08:50,463 --> 00:08:52,824
Asking me for money is called doing it by yourself?

140
00:08:52,824 --> 00:08:55,704
How can that be the same? What are we? We're brothers.

141
00:08:55,704 --> 00:09:00,664
Besides, I can let you borrow it after I buy it.

142
00:09:00,664 --> 00:09:02,948
I don't have money.

143
00:09:02,948 --> 00:09:05,983
Xiaowen. Xiaowen!

144
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,684
- Bin, where are you going?
- Something came up.

145
00:09:10,684 --> 00:09:12,260
- What thing?
- I want to go to the Senior Grade.

146
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:15,264
- For what? I need to talk to you about something.
- What is it then?

147
00:09:15,264 --> 00:09:16,883
- The plan.
- What plan?

148
00:09:16,883 --> 00:09:18,680
The track and field team's plan.

149
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,860
I know, I know. I'll definitely do it for you.

150
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:24,926
The entire country is preparing for the Olympic Games. Don't drop the ball!

151
00:09:24,926 --> 00:09:28,883
[Canteen]

152
00:09:28,883 --> 00:09:31,884
Gao Yang, Piao Jiutong is just a fraud.

153
00:09:31,884 --> 00:09:34,483
He still owes me ten yuan for the CD I sold him last time.

154
00:09:34,483 --> 00:09:38,804
You sold it? Jiabao, don't you cherish your disc the most? Why did you sell it?

155
00:09:38,804 --> 00:09:42,603
There's a competition in Linyang. I'm saving up for the entry fee.

156
00:09:42,603 --> 00:09:44,564
Is it an official competition this time?

157
00:09:44,564 --> 00:09:46,123
Don't get scammed of your entry fee again.

158
00:09:46,123 --> 00:09:47,444
This time is official for sure.

159
00:09:47,444 --> 00:09:50,091
What if your parents beat you up when they find out?

160
00:09:50,091 --> 00:09:52,430
If you guys don't tell them, how would they know?

161
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:54,584
But with your terrible voice, what song can you sing?

162
00:09:54,584 --> 00:09:56,564
How great it would be if you let me use your money to buy study materials.

163
00:09:56,564 --> 00:09:58,804
Your grades are terrible. It's more of a waste to buy study materials.

164
00:09:58,804 --> 00:10:00,243
I'm really serious this time.

165
00:10:00,243 --> 00:10:01,595
Yeah, right.

166
00:10:01,595 --> 00:10:05,335
By the way, Gao Yang, if you want to look at study materials, you can go to the library.

167
00:10:05,335 --> 00:10:08,740
The ones there won't work. I have to look at Wu Zhixun's notes.

168
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,603
Hello, Teacher.

169
00:10:16,603 --> 00:10:18,284
Did you two see Dawei?

170
00:10:18,284 --> 00:10:20,030
No.

171
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:21,903
No.

172
00:10:21,903 --> 00:10:24,160
Mr. Gao, why are you looking for him?

173
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,684
Tell me if you see Dawei.

174
00:10:27,684 --> 00:10:29,080
Okay.

175
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,300
Bye, Teacher.

176
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,940
Bye.

177
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:36,860
- Try this. Have a piece.
- Okay. Have one yourself.

178
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:38,624
- Reporting.
- All right.

179
00:10:38,624 --> 00:10:40,707
Xiaowen, what is it?

180
00:10:40,707 --> 00:10:42,404
It's nothing. Enjoy your lunch first.

181
00:10:42,404 --> 00:10:44,338
Come. Come here. Come here.

182
00:10:44,338 --> 00:10:46,090
What's going on? Go ahead.

183
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:52,444
Mr. Wu, I want to know if there was an alumnus named Wu Zhixun.

184
00:10:52,444 --> 00:10:54,444
Yes, he was my student.

185
00:10:54,444 --> 00:10:56,284
He got into Beijing University afterwards?

186
00:10:56,284 --> 00:10:58,204
Yes. What's wrong?

187
00:10:58,204 --> 00:11:03,323
I just want to know if he has any unique study methods.

188
00:11:03,323 --> 00:11:06,910
For example, study notes or something like that.

189
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:11,020
Yes, that... Go to the library

190
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:13,220
and look for Wu Zhixun's study notes. You'll find it there.

191
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:16,464
- The library?
- Yes, he donated them all to the school after he graduated.

192
00:11:16,464 --> 00:11:17,880
The notes are really nice and neat.

193
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,940
You can make a photocopy of them. Go look for it in the library.

194
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:21,793
Okay. Th-thank you, Teacher.

195
00:11:21,793 --> 00:11:23,704
It's nothing. Have you eaten? Want some?

196
00:11:23,704 --> 00:11:25,344
No, thank you.

197
00:11:25,344 --> 00:11:29,990
What a nice kid. He's looking for study notes instead of eating lunch.

198
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:33,110
Buy me dinner after school!

199
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:39,150
Hello, Mr. Gao.

200
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:43,763
- Hello, Mr. Gao.
- Hello, hello.

201
00:11:43,763 --> 00:11:45,350
Mr. Gao.

202
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:52,310
Dawei, I've been looking for you all day. Let's talk.

203
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:53,524
I'm busy.

204
00:11:53,524 --> 00:11:55,164
You're busy after school?

205
00:11:55,164 --> 00:11:56,444
I have tutoring for my senior year.

206
00:11:56,444 --> 00:11:58,690
Where are you getting tutored? I'll take you there.

207
00:12:08,250 --> 00:12:11,283
[Jenny's Salon]

208
00:12:11,283 --> 00:12:13,503
Sir, would you like to dye your hair?

209
00:12:13,503 --> 00:12:14,704
I just want a haircut.

210
00:12:14,704 --> 00:12:17,404
Our store has an event. If you apply for a VIP card, you get 20% off.

211
00:12:17,404 --> 00:12:19,489
Haohao, go hang up the towels. I'll take care of him.

212
00:12:19,489 --> 00:12:21,763
- Okay, okay.
- Go on.

213
00:12:21,763 --> 00:12:24,963
Sir, do you want a massage before we wash your hair?

214
00:12:24,963 --> 00:12:26,763
- Go ahead.
- All right.

215
00:12:26,763 --> 00:12:28,564
Sir, you've come to the right person for a massage.

216
00:12:28,564 --> 00:12:31,100
All my techniques are professional.

217
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,224
How does it feel, Sir? Does it feel good?

218
00:12:36,224 --> 00:12:37,444
Not bad.

219
00:12:37,444 --> 00:12:39,003
Alright, that'll be 5 Yuan.

220
00:12:39,003 --> 00:12:40,747
Wait, why are you charging extra? Isn't it within the wash, cut and blow-dry package?

221
00:12:40,747 --> 00:12:42,464
That doesn't include a massage.

222
00:12:42,464 --> 00:12:43,723
Well, you didn't tell me!

223
00:12:43,723 --> 00:12:46,004
- But you have to pay if you got the massage.
- Zhao Jiabao,

224
00:12:46,004 --> 00:12:47,280
what are you doing?

225
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,760
- Are you extorting money from the customer?
- I'm washing his hair.

226
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:51,556
No wonder business has been so bad lately.

227
00:12:51,556 --> 00:12:53,326
Zhao Dezhu, keep your son in line!

228
00:12:53,326 --> 00:12:54,950
- I'm washing his hair.
- He's extorting the customer!

229
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:56,979
Little Rascal! I'm sorry.

230
00:12:56,979 --> 00:12:59,690
- Get back here!
- I was washing his hair!
[Jenny's Salon]

231
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:02,260
Where did you learn extortion? Come back here!

232
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,960
Xiaowen, you're studying too?

233
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:31,970
Look, he solved this problem perfectly.

234
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:38,020
You still have a chance if you beg me.

235
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:44,383
This is Wu Zhixun's notes. It's real.

236
00:13:44,383 --> 00:13:46,854
Didn't you not have enough money?

237
00:13:46,854 --> 00:13:48,878
I borrowed it from Zhao Jiabao.

238
00:13:48,878 --> 00:13:51,590
Old buddies are better after all.

239
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,573
What are you looking at?

240
00:14:00,573 --> 00:14:02,280
Study notes.

241
00:14:02,894 --> 00:14:04,044
Whose study notes?

242
00:14:04,044 --> 00:14:06,430
Wu Zhixun's.

243
00:14:06,430 --> 00:14:09,080
How could it be Wu Zhixun's?

244
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,450
You must've gotten scammed.

245
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,603
It's fake. I could tell right away that's it's fake.

246
00:14:28,603 --> 00:14:30,723
Even the cover is not the same. Mine is leather, okay?

247
00:14:30,723 --> 00:14:32,960
You didn't even know you got scammed.

248
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:37,404
I photocopied the original at the library.

249
00:14:37,404 --> 00:14:39,090
It's fake!

250
00:14:40,062 --> 00:14:43,030
Just read the fake one. I have the real one with me.

251
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:47,243
That's enough. Being angry with him might just kill you.

252
00:14:47,243 --> 00:14:48,446
Stay out of this.

253
00:14:48,446 --> 00:14:49,963
You...

254
00:14:49,963 --> 00:14:52,084
Why do you need so much money?

255
00:14:52,084 --> 00:14:55,100
Are you still going to sign up for that stupid singing competition?

256
00:14:56,540 --> 00:14:57,566
N-No, I'm not.

257
00:14:57,566 --> 00:14:58,886
What do you need it for then?

258
00:14:58,886 --> 00:15:00,903
Why must you sing all the time?

259
00:15:00,903 --> 00:15:03,458
You're off-key when you speak, yet you still want to sing all the time.

260
00:15:03,458 --> 00:15:07,524
Jiabao, do you really think it's that easy to become a singer?

261
00:15:07,524 --> 00:15:09,905
Do you know how much hard work you have to put forth?

262
00:15:09,905 --> 00:15:11,564
Even so, you still might not make it.

263
00:15:11,564 --> 00:15:13,069
Take me as example.

264
00:15:13,069 --> 00:15:15,353
Since young, I trained through the coldest days in the winter and the hottest days in the summer.

265
00:15:15,353 --> 00:15:17,041
How many beatings did I take?

266
00:15:17,041 --> 00:15:19,363
What's the point of training from childhood?

267
00:15:19,363 --> 00:15:21,194
Look at this.

268
00:15:21,194 --> 00:15:23,963
Now, I can't even reach the customer when I do haircuts like this. What's the use of it?

269
00:15:23,963 --> 00:15:25,800
Don't I still have to change my profession?

270
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:28,195
We just don't want you to... help me up.

271
00:15:28,195 --> 00:15:30,711
How old are you now? Why are you making those moves?

272
00:15:30,711 --> 00:15:32,620
We just don't want you to make detours in life.

273
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:35,304
Why can't you understand?

274
00:15:35,304 --> 00:15:36,961
Haircut!

275
00:15:36,961 --> 00:15:38,900
Coming!

276
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:42,070
You!

277
00:15:42,070 --> 00:15:44,504
Take your dad's words to heart, okay?

278
00:15:44,504 --> 00:15:46,910
Do some self-reflection.

279
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:06,164
Xiaowen, don't blame me

280
00:16:06,164 --> 00:16:09,060
if you get a bad score on the exam for reading fake study notes.

281
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:25,780
Do you want to look at the real one?

282
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:33,423
Just directly tell me if you do.

283
00:16:33,423 --> 00:16:35,720
Why must you be so proud?

284
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:45,483
Are you going to study or not?

285
00:16:45,483 --> 00:16:46,603
I am studying.

286
00:16:46,603 --> 00:16:49,024
Then go and study in your room.

287
00:16:49,024 --> 00:16:51,784
But the atmosphere is better when we study together.

288
00:16:51,784 --> 00:16:54,610
I'm falling asleep in there by myself.

289
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,960
You can't understand it, right?

290
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:06,890
I won't mind if you explain it to me.

291
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,384
Which problem don't you understand?

292
00:17:09,384 --> 00:17:10,843
This one.

293
00:17:10,843 --> 00:17:13,924
What's this? I still don't understand it after staring at it for half the day.

294
00:17:13,924 --> 00:17:17,890
That's the one. Quickly explain it to me. Explain it to me.

295
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:23,583
This is a geometry problem.

296
00:17:23,583 --> 00:17:26,403
Solid geometry requires auxiliary lines.

297
00:17:26,403 --> 00:17:28,343
His solution is really logical.

298
00:17:28,343 --> 00:17:32,050
However, you have to pay attention to the auxiliary lines.

299
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:34,683
Let's look at this auxiliary line.

300
00:17:34,683 --> 00:17:39,024
it's an extension from Point C to Point D.

301
00:17:39,024 --> 00:17:41,844
It's not just a simple line.

302
00:17:41,844 --> 00:17:46,784
Actually, it can introduce a surface or a body into this space.

303
00:17:46,784 --> 00:17:50,650
For example, a tetrahedron or a pentahedron.

304
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,363
The auxiliary line...

305
00:17:54,363 --> 00:17:56,770
The auxiliary line...

306
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:02,730
The auxiliary line isn't just a simple line...

307
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:24,603
Why are you going to bed so early?

308
00:18:24,603 --> 00:18:28,260
I'll do better than you on tomorrow's exam.

309
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:36,180
Pass it back. No talking.

310
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:51,450
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

311
00:18:51,450 --> 00:18:58,718
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

312
00:18:58,718 --> 00:19:04,750
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

313
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:10,748
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

314
00:19:10,748 --> 00:19:12,463
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead  ♫

315
00:19:12,463 --> 00:19:14,984
Meng'er. Meng'er, let me copy it.

316
00:19:14,984 --> 00:19:17,460
♫  I will no longer run away  ♫

317
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:23,040
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

318
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:26,927
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

319
00:19:26,927 --> 00:19:30,275
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

320
00:19:30,275 --> 00:19:33,670
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

321
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:40,330
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

322
00:19:40,330 --> 00:19:43,641
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

323
00:19:43,641 --> 00:19:47,753
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

324
00:19:47,753 --> 00:19:51,573
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

325
00:19:51,573 --> 00:19:58,340
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫

326
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:19,024
Students, everyone says Class 3 ranks behind many classes in our grade.

327
00:20:19,024 --> 00:20:22,523
I always say that you're the worst class I've ever taught.

328
00:20:22,523 --> 00:20:25,903
But I was wrong about that. During this midterm,

329
00:20:25,903 --> 00:20:28,604
you all have made me see you in a new light!

330
00:20:28,604 --> 00:20:31,144
Our class made tremendous progress this time.

331
00:20:31,144 --> 00:20:35,023
Give yourselves a hand, everyone.

332
00:20:35,023 --> 00:20:38,703
One student in particular. His grades are normally not very high.

333
00:20:38,703 --> 00:20:41,764
But this time, his scores improved all the way to the top ten of our grade.

334
00:20:41,764 --> 00:20:46,345
The amount of improvement is rarely seen in the history of our school.

335
00:20:47,284 --> 00:20:49,004
Meng'er, is it you?

336
00:20:49,004 --> 00:20:50,783
No, it's not me. It's him.

337
00:20:50,783 --> 00:20:52,801
Look over here! Look over here!

338
00:20:53,843 --> 00:20:58,344
I'm sure you all know who he is. I hope everyone can learn from him.

339
00:20:58,344 --> 00:21:01,643
There's no need to learn from me. There's no need to learn from me.

340
00:21:01,643 --> 00:21:05,937
It was mainly because of my innate talent. It's easy if I'm determined to learn.

341
00:21:07,324 --> 00:21:09,269
Praise me.

342
00:21:10,244 --> 00:21:12,831
What are you doing? Are you insane?

343
00:21:13,818 --> 00:21:15,284
What? Aren't I in the top 10 of our grade?

344
00:21:15,284 --> 00:21:17,403
What do you mean top 10 of your grade? You even...

345
00:21:17,403 --> 00:21:19,864
Take those fake glasses off! I'm embarrassed for you!

346
00:21:19,864 --> 00:21:22,564
What top 10 of your grade.

347
00:21:22,564 --> 00:21:24,489
It wasn't me?

348
00:21:26,084 --> 00:21:28,163
Then who is it?

349
00:21:29,206 --> 00:21:31,403
[Certificate of Honor - Student Ye Xiaowen: Due to excellent grades, you are awarded as your grade's Top 10 student]

350
00:21:31,403 --> 00:21:33,329
Students,

351
00:21:33,329 --> 00:21:35,724
the ten students standing next to me

352
00:21:35,724 --> 00:21:38,843
are the ones who scored within the top 10

353
00:21:38,843 --> 00:21:41,824
on this midterm exam.

354
00:21:41,824 --> 00:21:45,303
I hope every student sitting here

355
00:21:45,303 --> 00:21:49,464
would gain valuable experience from these students.

356
00:21:49,464 --> 00:21:54,984
Let's welcome student representative, Ye Xiaowen, to come on stage and give a speech.

357
00:21:54,984 --> 00:21:56,481
Please welcome him.

358
00:22:08,004 --> 00:22:11,363
We need to persist with everything we do.

359
00:22:11,363 --> 00:22:13,929
I'm finished. Thank you.

360
00:22:18,984 --> 00:22:20,784
Bravo!

361
00:22:29,484 --> 00:22:31,123
Wait, is my notebook fake?

362
00:22:31,123 --> 00:22:34,024
Don't ask. You didn't study it.

363
00:22:34,024 --> 00:22:36,260
You're just one place ahead of me. Why are you so arrogant?

364
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:38,699
"We need to persist with everything we do."

365
00:22:38,699 --> 00:22:42,863
Ye Xiaowen's speech was concise and comprehensive. Very good.

366
00:22:42,863 --> 00:22:46,284
- My dad doesn't know what to say anymore.
- Next, I have some good news to announce.

367
00:22:46,284 --> 00:22:47,244
It's my turn! It's my turn!

368
00:22:47,244 --> 00:22:51,123
Zhao Jiabao from Grade 2, Class 3

369
00:22:51,123 --> 00:22:53,324
won first place

370
00:22:53,324 --> 00:22:58,883
- at the Original Song Contest for High School Students in Linyang.
- Wow!

371
00:22:59,603 --> 00:23:01,883
Jiabao, did you really win first place?

372
00:23:01,883 --> 00:23:03,680
Why? You've underestimated me, right?

373
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,103
He's from our class too.

374
00:23:05,103 --> 00:23:07,244
His grades are mediocre, but he's quite talented in that aspect.

375
00:23:07,244 --> 00:23:11,124
What song did you write? Let us hear it later.

376
00:23:13,643 --> 00:23:15,144
It's nothing. It's nothing.

377
00:23:15,144 --> 00:23:16,443
So stingy.

378
00:23:16,443 --> 00:23:20,623
Zhao Jiabao, please stand up and let everyone get to know you. Please.

379
00:23:30,643 --> 00:23:35,183
I've always been emphasizing that besides having good grades,

380
00:23:35,183 --> 00:23:38,943
students of our No.3 High School must develop their potential in all aspects.

381
00:23:39,403 --> 00:23:43,363
Life isn't just about taking exams.

382
00:23:43,363 --> 00:23:47,324
Zhao Jiaobao is a vivid example.

383
00:23:47,324 --> 00:23:52,184
Although he doesn't have ideal grades,

384
00:23:52,184 --> 00:23:56,064
he has a dream and is willing to work hard.

385
00:23:56,064 --> 00:24:00,623
He found himself through music and made a wonderful achievement.

386
00:24:00,623 --> 00:24:03,764
Let's all give him a round of applause.

387
00:24:15,979 --> 00:24:21,203
Jiajia, Meng'er, what do you want to eat today? Order whatever you want. Jiabao is buying today.

388
00:24:24,166 --> 00:24:26,486
[Award Certificate - Zhao Jiabao: 1st Place in the 2005 Linyang High School Singing Competition Bel Canto Group]

389
00:24:30,743 --> 00:24:32,683
I know, Zhao Jiabao.

390
00:24:32,683 --> 00:24:34,843
You won first place and you just won't stop bragging about it.

391
00:24:34,843 --> 00:24:37,664
Exactly. Don't keep showing off your certificate.

392
00:24:37,664 --> 00:24:39,720
Sing the song you sang at the time for us.

393
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:42,680
That's right. Liven things up.

394
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:45,044
Can you show some respect for the first-place winner?

395
00:24:45,044 --> 00:24:48,883
Mr. Wu said I will be a professional musician in the future. I have to protect my voice.

396
00:24:48,883 --> 00:24:52,104
Alright, he's being a diva already. Let's just order.

397
00:24:52,104 --> 00:24:55,084
Let's order this. Local chicken, spare ribs, and mushrooms for 5.

398
00:24:55,084 --> 00:24:58,204
By the way, Xiaowen, how did you do so well? You got into the top ten of our grade.

399
00:24:58,204 --> 00:25:00,764
Xiaowen, do you have any secrets for that?

400
00:25:00,764 --> 00:25:02,564
Was it because of Wu Zhixun's study notes?

401
00:25:02,564 --> 00:25:06,244
No, Xiaowen has been smart since his childhood.

402
00:25:06,244 --> 00:25:08,683
He will surely achieve what he sets his mind on.

403
00:25:08,683 --> 00:25:11,843
He's just been studying especially hard lately

404
00:25:11,843 --> 00:25:14,603
as if h-he's competing against someone.

405
00:25:14,603 --> 00:25:15,843
Who's he competing against?

406
00:25:15,843 --> 00:25:17,324
I'm not competing.

407
00:25:17,324 --> 00:25:20,369
The teachers in No.3 High School taught us well.

408
00:25:20,369 --> 00:25:21,380
Where's Gao Yang?

409
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:25,003
He said he's going to buy something. He'll be back soon.

410
00:25:27,403 --> 00:25:30,783
Did Gao Yang take it too hard?

411
00:25:30,783 --> 00:25:32,743
His grades weren't even as good as the last exam.

412
00:25:32,743 --> 00:25:37,403
Maybe he's hiding somewhere crying by himself now.

413
00:25:37,403 --> 00:25:40,403
Let's comfort him when he gets here.

414
00:26:22,944 --> 00:26:24,783
What is this, Gao Yang?

415
00:26:24,783 --> 00:26:26,123
What's up with you?

416
00:26:26,123 --> 00:26:29,883
From now on, I will be a musician.

417
00:26:37,624 --> 00:26:40,504
Dawei's Dad, thank you for letting me borrow your car last time.

418
00:26:40,504 --> 00:26:44,484
Don't mention it. Just let me know if you need to use the car again. They are all there.

419
00:26:44,484 --> 00:26:46,001
Sure.

420
00:26:47,340 --> 00:26:48,443
Look at you.

421
00:26:48,443 --> 00:26:51,363
Why did you bring so much food when you came to have a drink with me?

422
00:26:51,363 --> 00:26:54,483
Why? I don't have food here? You don't have to do that at all.

423
00:26:54,483 --> 00:26:57,560
No, I'm not just here to drink today.

424
00:26:57,560 --> 00:27:01,099
It's sort of a home visit too.

425
00:27:01,099 --> 00:27:03,101
A home visit?

426
00:27:03,101 --> 00:27:04,203
Did Dawei get into trouble again?

427
00:27:04,203 --> 00:27:06,284
No, no. Don't be nervous.

428
00:27:06,284 --> 00:27:09,903
I just want to talk about the soccer team.

429
00:27:09,903 --> 00:27:15,524
I'm responsible for Dawei's expulsion from the soccer team.

430
00:27:16,163 --> 00:27:18,844
At the time, something came up at home,

431
00:27:18,844 --> 00:27:20,804
so I didn't have time to handle his matter.

432
00:27:20,804 --> 00:27:24,044
I want to apologize to you for that. I'm sorry.

433
00:27:24,044 --> 00:27:26,524
Mr. Gao, please don't say that.

434
00:27:26,524 --> 00:27:28,603
Dawei shouldn't have fought with someone.

435
00:27:28,603 --> 00:27:32,324
Besides, this has nothing to do with you.

436
00:27:32,324 --> 00:27:35,692
Boys just tend to cause trouble. He's just hard to raise.

437
00:27:35,692 --> 00:27:37,284
Please understand.

438
00:27:37,284 --> 00:27:39,564
No, I agree with that wholeheartedly.

439
00:27:39,564 --> 00:27:41,683
Take my son Gao Yang for example,

440
00:27:41,683 --> 00:27:45,984
he had his mind set on going to Beijing a while ago.

441
00:27:45,984 --> 00:27:47,163
After I convinced him,

442
00:27:47,163 --> 00:27:49,864
he said, "Fine, I'll go to a school in Beijing with my own efforts."

443
00:27:49,864 --> 00:27:51,883
I said, "That's great!"

444
00:27:51,883 --> 00:27:55,743
But today, he asked me for money to buy a guitar.

445
00:27:55,743 --> 00:27:59,784
I asked him why. He said, "I'm not studying anymore. I want to take the admission exams for the arts."

446
00:27:59,784 --> 00:28:04,404
I must say, I can't do anything about that child at all. He can't persist with anything.

447
00:28:04,404 --> 00:28:07,443
Dawei is just the opposite of your son.

448
00:28:07,443 --> 00:28:11,743
This boy loves sports since he was a child, especially soccer.

449
00:28:11,743 --> 00:28:15,423
Ever since he can't play soccer, he completely changed.

450
00:28:15,423 --> 00:28:17,764
He pulls a long face everyday and he's developing a bad temper.

451
00:28:17,764 --> 00:28:21,284
Sometimes he would flip out and yell at me. What do you think I should do?

452
00:28:21,284 --> 00:28:23,505
Dawei's Dad,

453
00:28:23,505 --> 00:28:27,764
after all, he's going through puberty. Be more understanding.

454
00:28:27,764 --> 00:28:33,043
Dawei will be taking the college entrance exam soon. If you need anything, just tell me anytime.

455
00:28:33,043 --> 00:28:36,163
Mr. Gao, thank you so much.

456
00:28:36,163 --> 00:28:39,463
In my opinion, anyone's child who has such a great teacher

457
00:28:39,463 --> 00:28:41,464
is truly like having cyan smoke coming off the ancestor's grave (indicates good luck).

458
00:28:41,464 --> 00:28:43,363
- Please don't say that.
- It's true!

459
00:28:43,363 --> 00:28:45,160
It's true! Here, come on. I'll give you a toast.

460
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:47,109
Thank you.

461
00:28:58,764 --> 00:29:01,384
Gao Yang, practice that later.

462
00:29:01,384 --> 00:29:02,923
- Eat something first.
- I can't.

463
00:29:02,923 --> 00:29:04,734
It's a difficult task within a short time. I'm about to take the entrance exam for art colleges.

464
00:29:04,734 --> 00:29:07,273
Do you have a musical talent?

465
00:29:07,964 --> 00:29:10,364
I have plenty of musical talents.

466
00:29:10,364 --> 00:29:13,931
Look at my hands. They are so slender and long.

467
00:29:13,931 --> 00:29:18,024
Even the guitar seller said I was born to play guitar.

468
00:29:18,024 --> 00:29:21,104
Jiabao, you're lucky now. Form a band with me.

469
00:29:21,104 --> 00:29:26,164
I'm learning to sing, too. Let me join your band as well.

470
00:29:26,164 --> 00:29:29,663
You and your younger brother are singing folk songs from the Korean Nationality, okay?

471
00:29:29,663 --> 00:29:31,936
What are we playing?

472
00:29:31,936 --> 00:29:33,203
Rock and roll,

473
00:29:33,203 --> 00:29:35,283
Rock.

474
00:29:35,284 --> 00:29:37,123
I can switch to rock and roll too.

475
00:29:37,123 --> 00:29:41,983
Beibei, Gao Yang is just acting up. Can you not cheer him on?

476
00:29:41,983 --> 00:29:43,945
Who's acting up?

477
00:29:44,764 --> 00:29:46,401
Alright,

478
00:29:47,703 --> 00:29:49,144
I'll make a toast.

479
00:29:49,144 --> 00:29:53,524
Well, Xiaowen has good grades. Jiabao won first place.

480
00:29:53,524 --> 00:29:56,744
As for me, I'm about to become a musician.

481
00:29:56,744 --> 00:29:59,883
I wish everyone a bright future.

482
00:29:59,883 --> 00:30:01,383
Come on.

483
00:30:03,224 --> 00:30:04,343
You guys eat first.

484
00:30:04,343 --> 00:30:06,098
I'm leaving now.

485
00:30:07,123 --> 00:30:08,683
What's wrong with Xiaowen?

486
00:30:08,683 --> 00:30:11,964
Xiaowen hates people who give up half way.

487
00:30:11,964 --> 00:30:13,403
I'll go check on him.

488
00:30:13,403 --> 00:30:14,484
Okay, quickly go.

489
00:30:14,484 --> 00:30:16,883
Wait, who's giving up half way?

490
00:30:16,883 --> 00:30:18,901
Xiaowen!

491
00:30:22,343 --> 00:30:24,724
Xiaowen, eat something.

492
00:30:24,724 --> 00:30:26,955
You didn't each much just now.

493
00:30:32,123 --> 00:30:35,824
Xiaowen, don't be mad.

494
00:30:36,724 --> 00:30:38,439
I'm not.

495
